      "type": "exclusivity-notice",
      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "Exclusivity Notice",
        "body": "Our Children’s Couture mirrors the exact precision and standard of excellence found in our adult collections, elevating the youngest visionaries. We invite you to experience this distinction through two exclusive avenues:                 \n\n      1. The Bespoke Journey\nSecure their legacy with a distinct, tailored-to-order masterpiece. Each garment is drafted to your child's unique blueprint, available exclusively through private Atelier consultation.\n\n2. The Atelier Curated Collection\nFor those seeking immediate distinction, we maintain a highly limited selection of already-made designs and exclusive runway samples. These miniature works of art are available for immediate acquisition within the sanctuary of the Nancy Vuu Atelier."
      }
